00:26:37.350 --> 00:26:40.460
you know, we have these
freedoms but we're also wanting,

00:26:40.460 --> 00:26:41.850
we're talking about our identities.

00:26:41.850 --> 00:26:45.170
Now, we're also wanting to kind
